wiki.summary: "Hotel Lobby (Unc & Phew)" is a song by American rappers Quavo and Takeoff of the hip hop group Migos. It was released on May 20, 2022 and is their first release as the duo Unc & Phew. The song was produced by Murda Beatz, Keanu Beats and Fabio Aguilar. It is released as the first single off their collaborative album Only Built for Infinity Links. Read more on Last.fm.
